{"tid":533839,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【打擊供應】林奮強籲8年禁租售期助上車 香討網民：樓價長升長有","createTime":"2018-01-19T08:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T07:21:54.000Z","uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f0a674b0c779205f980cd225a80265e068634f","tid":533839,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:16:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180119/57727588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57727588&d=Q2wpGJvAxivVVMlKozuYraNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=fe0d9be5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57727588&h=0c387dd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180119/57727588</a><br />\n<br />\n樓價長升長有，梁振英任內由打擊供應著手，物業買賣設3年禁售期，鎖死二手供應，加上按揭成數上限和發展商高成數按揭及優惠，供不應求下購買力全湧入一手市場，樓價火箭式上升。持有多項物業、梁粉「行會樓王」前行政會議成員林奮強今於報章專欄更呼籲，將禁售期擴至8年，同時禁租，以「協助上車」，向來屬樓市好友的香討網民，解讀為支持樓市措施，歡呼「長升長有」、「二手樓租金仲唔大爆升？」<br />\n<br />\n林奮強於《經濟日報》專欄文章中稱，現時推動樓價上升原因為租金上揚，並呼籲，禁止發展商為新盤提供高成數按揭、指定樓價（如2,000萬）以下單位按揭成數上限上調至8成，並設立8年禁租禁售期，以壓抑投資需求。然而林於同篇文章聲稱，香港樓市的投資價值極有限，「各項印花稅『辣招』下，投機行為其實早已絕迹」。<br />\n<br />\n香港討論區網民言論：<br />\n你假誠：讚（贊）成。繼續鎖盤。長升長有。<br />\nfalconV8：這樣做法，咪一樣令樓價急升。<br />\n=租樓日日賺=：8年禁租，正呀！現有二手樓租金仲唔大爆升？林奮強梗係想自己手上幾十間收租樓租金火箭升空啦！<br />\n崖上純情的主席：直接禁止買賣物業把啦。<br />\n電腦怪傑：想夾死租淡。<br />\nannabb：痴（黐）線，大把發展商唔租唔賣十幾年，冇新租盤，仲禁租？？冇腦，禁租再加空置稅，就有得諗。"},{"pid":"5c79535ea002da8459c22989a87ef1950d90f0e9","tid":533839,"uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/162648_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F162648_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3903504f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n師父會唔會租唔到屋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf8f6ece0e2669ebf7144783f6d3594bc64dfdf","tid":533839,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"有幾癡線先可以講出呢d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a437f2986bcabe6f25a93737a5c4e4e67627e1d","tid":533839,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"根本條友就係唔想個市跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcb34cda5f915064c4307657c54ffbf0d6b874d","tid":533839,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:58:14.000Z","msg":"經過多重辣招之後，真係仲有人炒樓咩？<br />\n自住需求真心大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c31357fe9ffd6561efbc081bc6319562ad8741","tid":533839,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"打殘所有租售市場，停起公共房屋<br />\n香港人只可以做樓奴，上大陸住，移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff10bcfd635fe410f8f0e80389bceb4dfe1761a","tid":533839,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:42:31.000Z","msg":"8萬五重推已經嚇到好友腳震賴屎"},{"pid":"fb785e89761f019e6647d24303ee6d812ae86acb","tid":533839,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c31357fe9ffd6561efbc081bc6319562ad8741","tid":533839,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"打殘所有租售市場，停起公共房屋<br />\n香港人只可以做樓奴，上大陸住，移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"港共不知幾想咁<br />\n但自由經濟又好重要"},{"pid":"62efababf447960ec92d7a6c2c69c1cafca47d64","tid":533839,"uid":35870,"like":0